title: Edmund Fletcher
text:
Edmund Fletcher was an <a href="University%20of%20Oxford">Oxford</a> <a href="Colleges%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Oxford">college</a> <a href="Chief%20executive%20officer">head</a> in the <a href="16th-century">16th-century</a>.
Fletcher was educated at <a href="Exeter%20College%2C%20Oxford">Exeter College, Oxford</a>; and was <a href="List%20of%20Rectors%20of%20Exeter%20College%2C%20Oxford">Rector of Exeter College, Oxford</a> from 1526 to 1529. He was also <a href="Chaplain">Chaplain</a> to the <a href="University%20of%20Oxford">University</a>.
